\id 3JN - Kobon NT [kpw] -Papua New Guinea 2005 (web version -2013 bd)
\h 3 Jon
\toc1 Jon köp hain nɨbö u kalɨ kƚiñ rɨka
\toc2 3 Jon
\toc3 3Jn
\mt1 3 Jon
\mt2 Jon köp hain nɨbö u kalɨ kƚiñ rɨka
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Yad nɨbi bɨ Jisas Krais nɨp nɨŋ udpal gau kalɨp abad mɨdpin.
\p Nöp bɨ nɨŋeb aij yad Gaias köp i kalɨ kƚiñ rɨkabin. Yad nöp mɨdmagö yabɨƚ lɨbin. \x * \xo 1:1 \xt Ap 19:29; Ro 16:23\x*
\v 2 Mɨdamam aij yad. Yad God nɨp sabe gem hagpin, “Gaias nɨp abad mɨdaimön, nɨp mɨña nan ap gagnɨm, mɨd aij gɨnɨm,” a gɨpin. Yad nɨŋbin, ne ana ne aŋ daŋ mɨd aij gɨpan.
\v 3 Krais nɨbi bɨ añ mam rɨmnap aui apöm, ne Jisas Krais manö nɨŋö nɨŋ ud pɨdöŋ gɨmön, hagöp rö nöp göl gɨ mɨdpan, a geila u, yad mɨñ mɨñ yabɨƚ gɨpin. \x * \xo 1:3 \xt 2Jn 4\x*
\v 4 Ñɨ pai yad gau, Jisas Krais manö nɨŋö hagöp rö nöp gɨpal, a gɨnaböl u, yad mɨñ mɨñ yabɨƚ gɨnabin.
\s1 Gaias gɨ aij ga u nɨŋöm, Jon mɨñ mɨñ yabɨƚ ga
\p 
\v 5 Mɨdamam aij yad. Yad nɨŋbin, Jisas Krais hagöp rö nöp gɨmön, Krais nɨbi bɨ añ mam rɨmnap kalɨp pör ud aij yabɨƚ gɨpan. Añ mam ram mɨnöŋ mɨlö kub gau nɨbö nɨŋagpan gau, kalɨp haƚöwaƚö udmön, abad mɨd aij gɨpan.
\v 6 Krais nɨbi bɨ kalɨp anɨg gɨpan gau rɨmnap apöm, Krais nɨbi bɨ cöc aui mɨdpal kalɨp hagla, “Gaias Krais nɨbi bɨ nɨpe gau kalɨp mɨdmagö yabɨƚ löp,” a gɨla. Nɨbi bɨ God wög gɨ ajpal anɨb gau ud aij gɨ dammön, kale ram mɨnöŋ ke nɨbö ap arnɨg gɨnaböl u, nan gɨ ñeb rɨmnap kalɨp ñɨmön. Nan kalɨp ñɨnabön u kale udöm, gau ajöm, God nɨp wög göm, nan magö rauöm ñɨŋnaböl. \x * \xo 1:6 \xt Dai 3:13\x*
\v 7 Kale Jisas Krais manö aij u hag ñɨ ajöl gɨ, nɨbi bɨ Krais nɨp nɨŋ udagpal gau kalɨp hag nɨŋöm, nan magö nan gau udagpal. \x * \xo 1:7 \xt 1Ko 9:12\x*
\v 8 Anɨb u, nɨbi bɨ aij anɨbu rö kalɨp ud aij gun, nan rɨmnap ñun, aip jɨm ñun, Jisas Krais manö nɨŋö wög u gɨno, ar aij gɨnab.
\s1 Daiodrepis gɨ naij ga
\p 
\v 9 Yad Krais nɨbi bɨ mɨdpim gau kalöp köp ap kalɨ kƚiñ rɨknö u pen bɨ Daiodrepis, bɨ kub mɨdeinam, a göm, manö yad hagabin hag hain göm nɨŋagab.
\v 10 Anɨb u, yad mɨdpim u amem, nɨpe manö naij hagöm, hanɨp hag juöp manö u hagnabin. Pen anɨbu nöp wasö; nɨpe Krais nɨbi bɨ añ mam God Manö hag ñɨ ajpal gau kalɨp udagöm, nɨbi bɨ rɨmnap añ mam gau kalɨp udnɨg gɨlö, nɨpe wasö göm, anɨg gɨmim cöc i hainö auagmim, a göp.
\s1 Demidrias gɨ aij ga
\p 
\v 11 Mɨdamam aij yad. Nɨbi bɨ rɨmnap nagɨ ubɨŋ naij adö u hain gaiöl, ne unbö rö gagmön. Pen nɨbi bɨ rɨmnap nagɨ ubɨŋ aij adö u hain gaiöl, ne unbö rö gɨmön. Nɨbi bɨ nagɨ ubɨŋ aij adö u hain gɨpal gau, God ñɨ pai nɨpe mɨdpal. Nɨbi bɨ nagɨ ubɨŋ naij adö u hain gɨpal gau, kale God nɨp nɨŋagpal. \x * \xo 1:11 \xt 1Jn 3:6-10\x*
\p 
\v 12 Nɨbi bɨ magöŋhalö Demidrias nɨp nɨŋöm, bɨ aij, a gɨpal. Demidrias nɨpe Jisas Krais manö nɨŋö u hagöp rö gab u me, nɨpe bɨ aij u waiö lö nɨŋbun. Yad u rö nöp Demidrias nɨpe bɨ aij, a gabin. Ne nɨŋban, yad manö nɨhön hagnabin manö nɨŋö nöp hagnabin.
\s1 Manö magö adɨŋ rɨmnap
\p 
\v 13 Yad nöp manö iru nöp kalɨ kƚiñ rɨkbnep u pen köp ñɨg ig nöp rɨkagnabin; \x * \xo 1:13 \xt 2Jn 12\x*
\v 14-15 söl mɨdöp, yad ke amem, nöp mulu adɨŋ nɨŋem, aip asɨk mɨdul manö hagnabul.
\p God nöp abad mɨdö, agamɨj mɨdaimön. Mɨdamam gai i mɨdpal nöp, “Mɨdpan?” a gaböl. Mɨdamam ne aip mɨdpim gau kalɨp magöŋhalö, “Jon kalöp hagöp, ‘Mɨdpim?’ a göp,” a gɨmön. 
